OL,7,FA number of prisoners released early
OL,8,Fas part of a government's plan to
OL,9,Freduce overcrowding in jails were let
OL,10,Fout by mistake, the Ministry of
OL,11,FJustice has admitted.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, 10 September, some 1700
OL,14,Fprisoners were released as part of the
OL,15,Fscheme, along with the 1,000 normally
OL,16,Ffreed every week in England and Wales.
