OL,7,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Public safety is our first
OL,9,Fpriority. That is why we took decisive
OL,10,Faction to fix the broken prison system
OL,11,Fwe inherited and keep the most
OL,12,Fdangerous offenders locked up," a
OL,13,FMinistry of Justice spokesperson said.
OL,15,F"This included blocking the early
OL,16,Frelease of domestic abuse offences
OL,17,Fsuch as stalking and controlling
OL,18,Fbehaviour.
