OL,7,F"We are working with the police to
OL,8,Furgently return a very small number of
OL,9,Foffenders - who were charged
OL,10,Fincorrectly and sentenced under
OL,11,Frepealed legislation - to custody.
OL,13,F"The convictions remain valid with
OL,14,Foffenders monitored since their
OL,15,Frelease and will soon be back behind
OL,16,Fbars."
