OL,5,Cadmits
OL,7,FThe policy does not apply to those
OL,8,Fconvicted of sex offences, terrorism,
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse or some violent
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,13,Fpreviously admitted the decision to
OL,14,Frelease some prisoners early is not
OL,15,Fone the government "wanted to make,
OL,16,Fbut it was the only option left on the
OL,17,Ftable because the alternative would
OL,18,Fhave seen the total collapse of the
OL,19,Fcriminal justice system in this
OL,20,Fcountry".
