OL,7,FOn August 30, some 88,350 people were
OL,8,Fin prison, spiking to the highest
OL,9,Flevel ever recorded. Without any
OL,10,Fchanges, it was predicted there would
OL,11,Fbe almost 100,000 prisoners by 2025.
OL,13,FThe official usable capacity is
OL,14,Fcurrently 88,895, but several new
OL,15,Fjails are being built and the Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment has promised to increase
OL,17,Fconstruction.
